    "en": {
      "title": "The increased water charges are effective from today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The revision of the increased water charges will be effective from today (01). The gazette announcement related to the revision of water charges was issued by the Minister of Water Supply Mr. Keheliya Rambukwella on August 25. This time the revision of water charges has been done under 12 customer categories."
